<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!DOCTYPE paragraph PUBLIC "-//IFRS//DTD DITA Paragraph//EN" "../../../DocTypes/com.ifrs.doctype/dtd/paragraph.dtd"><paragraph id="IAS19_155" base="F16152932" principles="yes"><paranum class="- topic/title paragraph/paranum "/><titlealts><navtitle>155</navtitle></titlealts><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 19"/><data name="paranum" value="155"/></prolog><body outputclass="bold"><p id="IAS19_P0699">In recognising and measuring the surplus or deficit in an other long‑term employee benefit plan, an entity shall apply <xref id="IAS19_X0495" base="F16227989" href="IAS19_56.dita#IAS19_56">paragraphs 56–98</xref> and <xref id="IAS19_X0496" base="F16227990" href="IAS19_113.dita#IAS19_113">113–115</xref>. An entity shall apply <xref id="IAS19_X0497" base="F16227991" href="IAS19_116.dita#IAS19_116">paragraphs 116–119</xref> in recognising and measuring any reimbursement right.</p></body></paragraph>